Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:05.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fnArial\\b1\shad3\pos(640,550)}The day before summer vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.56,0:00:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamio Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to give you a name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy was on the embankment when we were going home from school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.90,0:00:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A puppet show like that isn't popular nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.62,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's name you Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the place where I always gaze at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're friends when we're like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunset is pretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could play like that with someone too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Byebye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that black thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He followed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's too small and can't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing a thing like this became your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave it a name, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.79,0:03:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, that was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want a pet, get a cat or a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be depressed if something like this wanders around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say hello to Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy was really angry, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let you stay in my room secretly for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's both apologise to Mummy tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking of asking someone in my class this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But will they play with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try practising it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to play with me during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it has to be in the afternoon though because I have supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll swim in the ocean, play cards, play with fireworks, and also do homework together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easy for me since I'm just copying all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back at noon, so play by yourself until then, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go too far away though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, a crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew, it's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It came over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't bully you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it off yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I'll be able to use magic if I take it off once I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There are cars and things on the road, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, let's go to the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My swimsuit this year is really revealing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it back. Hold it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora, it seems I'll be alone this summer too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't find anyone to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because everyone knows that I'm not a normal child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll do something really fun by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.27,0:06:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make my free assignment a diary and write down everything that was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the person from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I don't want to be all alone after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be the only one all alone in the long summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll try talking to that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If he seems nice, I'll try asking him to play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Smile. Smile. Act natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramen Set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are there more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,More?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,MORE?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me say it three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means that it was that shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you said it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you seem to have guts, and I don't dislike that part of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Yukito-san is a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let him stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very serious, not just seriously serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say Kunisaki Yukito?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be friendly towards Misuzu, but she hasn't had those attacks yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He might be able to become Misuzu's friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't had a friend all this time because of her illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be a bad guy, so I want to try betting on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have any other ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest are too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.19,0:08:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy and Yukito-san have work, and I have supplemental classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch the house, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought this; now what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's going to be a festival here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The tenth summer festival since that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I still remember it well after all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat in front of where they were selling chicks and talked to them for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,saying "Gao! Gao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl thought that if she brought a chick up, it would become a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if one did raise a chick that was brought at a fair, there's no way it would grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to take her hand and drag her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:10:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She was raised an obedient girl, but she just stared at me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and said "I want this" really longingly, just that one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu wasn't wanted at birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the child of two people who weren't even married, born amidst many fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My older sister died, leaving him and the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The man, who was left, pushed his own daughter onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It was really troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow lived on believing that one of these days, that man will return for his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, spending long hours with Misuzu,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,who is easily flustered and acts clumsily,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but always laughs and forgets that, made me laugh too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite all that, I'm not her parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That man might come any day to take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll have no choice but to revert to my solitary existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I maintained my own way of life so that I won't be too miserable when we eventually part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I haven't ever given her a present, not even on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended to forget each year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I debated what to do this year too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to become a real family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember definitely seeing that person and this scene somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the cicadas came in from the ventilation fan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the soy sauce container fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah, the salad oil spilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san's bacon egg is all ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't taste like cicadas?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish that Saika-oneechan gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.19,0:12:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there really a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God is watching over Saika and Maika right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He will definitely grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.72,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It was walking by itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's brand new.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave it here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is God's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have a home, will you come to the station with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you can definitely become good friends with Michiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also eat as much food as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultra-happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you have somewhere to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do your best,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so that one day, you can fly with those wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Try thinking about the one who has to be called to school each time you have an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine when you're with that freeloader, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you had got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm returning to work, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing you trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy was angry, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, she came to school so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san is probably waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's worrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be as natural as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.90,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make it seem like I was just careless and forgot to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because I want Yukito-san to think I'm a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.12,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hooome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,apparently Yukito-san left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to spend more time with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But he said he'll walk me to and from school like before,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so I just have to live with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still see him every day from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, my back sometimes hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you end up taking Misuzu in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why she isn't getting the love she needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Realise it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only parent she has!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't have to be so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known that for a long time, even without being told.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do I have to live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fearing she might disappear any day and not giving her any presents even on her birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make her my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ride into Tachibana's house and negotiate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I'll drift around, travelling alone on a hot springs tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do about Misuzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If I stay with you any longer, neither of us will be saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I've decided to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun spending the summer vacation with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.79,0:17:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Byebye, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll really be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do my best anymore if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go on a voyage too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.45,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, I won't have to part with Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I want to leave this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're alone, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.59,0:17:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best, even if I'm alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a strong girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all alone now,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,really all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.99,0:18:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was all alone until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be the same starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, even if I try my best, I just cause other people trouble, and nothing good ever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have kept on giving up like before,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,without loving anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.04,0:19:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I never wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I've finally realised.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was happy, just being by your side and seeing you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I couldn't get up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was once a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a human called Kunisaki Yukito,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was by Misuzu's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm healthy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can try my hardest again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try my best, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So don't go anywhere anymore. Stay by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a strong girl, so you'll be able to reach, for sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a goal no one has ever been able to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reach it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.62,0:21:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be by your side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.80,0:21:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind is starting to blur again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Misuzu, I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.85,0:21:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try our best, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we reach our goal, let's try our best, okay, Misuzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.57,0:21:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do our best, Yukito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.35,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I cut it to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it up to you, Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.40,0:23:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum went far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.24,0:23:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:24:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If she says at that time that she doesn't want to be with me anymore, then I won't mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.17,0:24:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao.
